title:
Day 1 : Lima - Paracas 
Very early in the morning, we will pick you up from the hotel to take you to the bus station, and start the 4 hours’ journey until Pisco’s airport, to live an amazing adventure of 1:30 hours over the mysterious Nazca Lines. During the flight, you will see impressive figures as the monkey, the spider, the Cóndor, and a lot of different drawings on these wonderful pampas. After this magical experience, you will be transferred to your hotel in Paracas, to have a well-deserved afternoon rest.
